          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-1 text-xs text-white/50 lg:justify-start sm:text-sm">
            <span>No obligation</span>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline">&middot;</span>
            <span>10-minute treatment</span>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline">&middot;</span>
            <span>Natural results</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Board certified badge -->
          <div class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Board-Certified Physician &middot; Every Injection by Dr. Menon</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== TRUST BAR (Purple) ========== -->
  <section class="bg-purple py-3.5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm font-medium text-white sm:text-base">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          Same-Week Appointments
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          Medical-Grade Expertise
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          State of the Art Equipment
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ========== PAIN POINTS ========== -->
  <section class="animate-on-scroll bg-cream py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-navy sm:text-4xl">
        Tired of Seeing Someone Older<br class="hidden sm:inline" /> in the Mirror?
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-text-muted">
        You're not alone. These are the frustrations that bring patients to Dr. Menon's door.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          { title: "Forehead lines that won't quit", desc: "No amount of skincare can relax the muscles causing those stubborn creases." },
          { title: "Crow's feet stealing your confidence", desc: "You notice them in every photo and video call — and you can't un-see them." },
          { title: "Frown lines making you look angry", desc: "People ask if you're upset when you're perfectly fine. It's exhausting." },
          { title: "Fear of looking \"done\"", desc: "You've seen bad Botox and you don't want that for yourself. We get it." },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-cream-dark bg-white p-6 text-left shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-navy">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-muted">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-text-muted">
        That's exactly why Dr. Menon takes a different approach. As a Board-Certified physician who personally performs every injection, she combines <strong class="text-navy">medical precision with an artistic eye</strong> — so you look like yourself, just refreshed.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== BEFORE / AFTER ========== -->
  <section class="animate-on-scroll bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-navy sm:text-4xl">
          See the Difference Expert Hands Make
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-text-muted">Real patients. Real results. Every treatment performed by Dr. Menon.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-4xl gap-6 sm:grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="ba-card overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-md">
